summary: This document details the arrest of Alfredo Rodriguez on December 15, 2009, pursuant to a warrant for obstruction of justice. The arrest was executed in Beach, Florida, and Rodriguez was subsequently transported to the Palm Beach County Jail.

persons.name: Alfredo Rodriguez

persons.name: Linnea R. Johnson

keyFacts: Alfredo Rodriguez was arrested on December 15, 2009, for obstruction of justice.
The arrest warrant was issued by United States Magistrate Judge Linnea R. Johnson.
Rodriguez was arrested without incident and transported to the Palm Beach County Jail.
